data.description: Seller's loss is your gain!! Relocation makes this lovely home now available! Sunny Brook is just that, this home offers a country setting on water and a close in location to Alexandria. Set on a 1+ acre newly landscaped lot & a river/creek runs through it! It is a spacious and open 3 bedroom, 2 bath, with a main floor laundry & a 2.5 oversized car garage. New carpet in the main floor bedrooms. The naturally lit full lower level offers another bedroom, bath and lots of room for storage. The neighborhood shares in the ownership and maintaining of the lot in the center of the development. It is great for kids of all ages, pets, neighborhood get togethers. Watch the Arrowood fireworks right from your driveway, sunsets from the dock or mosey down to the golf course, or better yet grab a paddle and your kayak and head towards Lake Charlie or Louise while the rest fish from the dock.  Retreat to this home and survey your domain from the deck, dock or the hammock! It's one for the short list.
